 ✅ 9) DOM (Document Object Model) ⭐⭐

DOM is a tree-like representation of HTML that allows JavaScript to access and modify web pages.

👉 Browser converts HTML → DOM Tree
Why DOM is Needed?
Without DOM:
❌ JavaScript cannot change HTML
With DOM:
✅ Change content
✅ Change style
✅ Handle events

