#### ❓ Q3. Difference between <div> and <section>?

Answer:

<div> → non-semantic container

 Non-semantic
 Used only for grouping or styling
 Has no meaning



<section> → semantic grouping of related content

 Semantic
 Represents a logical section of content
 Usually has a heading



📌 QC expects: Use section when content has meaning.



